2026-04-16 20:57:11 - llm.aliyun_llm - INFO - 收到 LLM API 响应  result={'choices': [{'message': {'content': '我理解我的角色：我是 PM（产品经理），需要检查邮箱、处理任务邮件、撰写产品规格文档。让我按工作流程逐步执行。\n\n## Step 1 — 读取邮箱', 'reasoning_content': "Let me understand my role and task:\n\n1. I am a PM (Product Manager) digital employee\n2. I need to check my mailbox for task_assign messages\n3. If there's a task, I need to follow the workflow: read mail → load product design spec → read requirements → write product spec → write to shared workspace → notify Manager → mark message done\n\nLet me start by checking my mailbox.", 'role': 'assistant', 'tool_calls': [{'function': {'arguments': '{"skill_name": "mailbox", "task_context": "读取 PM 邮箱，检查是否有 task_assign 类型的任务邮件。需要执行命令：python3 /workspace/skills/mailbox/scripts/mailbox_cli.py read --mailboxes-dir /mnt/shared/mailboxes --role pm。返回结果应包含消息列表，如果有 task_assign 消息则记录消息ID和任务内容。"}', 'name': 'skill_loader'}, 'id': 'tool-409cff9de62a483da9175b93a5173749', 'index': 0, 'type': 'function'}]}, 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'index': 0, 'logprobs': None}], 'object': 'chat.completion', 'usage': {'prompt_tokens': 4055, 'completion_tokens': 210, 'total_tokens': 4265, 'completion_tokens_details': {'reasoning_tokens': 84}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 0}}, 'created': 1776344231, 'system_fingerprint': None, 'model': 'glm-5.1', 'id': 'chatcmpl-611e4235-165b-99f2-bd08-ff527b6a7958'}
