2026-04-16 20:58:01 - llm.aliyun_llm - INFO - 收到 LLM API 响应  result={'choices': [{'message': {'content': '收到任务邮件！消息ID：`a37a8527-98d6-41b6-b666-d4edebd268d0`，任务是设计 XiaoPaw 宠物健康记录功能的产品规格文档。\n\n接下来，我需要同时加载产品文档规范和读取需求文档。', 'reasoning_content': 'I received a task_assign email from Manager. The task is to design a product spec document for "XiaoPaw 宠物健康记录功能". I need to:\n\n1. Record the message ID: a37a8527-98d6-41b6-b666-d4edebd268d0\n2. Load product_design skill (reference type)\n3. Read the requirements document at /mnt/shared/needs/requirements.md\n4. Write the product spec document\n5. Write it to /mnt/shared/design/product_spec.md\n6. Send task_done email to Manager\n7. Mark the original message as done\n\nLet me proceed step by step. Next, I need to load the product_design skill and read the requirements document. These two can be done in parallel since they\'re independent.', 'role': 'assistant', 'tool_calls': [{'function': {'arguments': '{"skill_name": "product_design", "task_context": ""}', 'name': 'skill_loader'}, 'id': 'tool-e608ce2fb1c7445db5b9b2a999fd34e5', 'index': 0, 'type': 'function'}, {'function': {'arguments': '{"skill_name": "mailbox", "task_context": "读取需求文档 /mnt/shared/needs/requirements.md 的内容。需要在沙盒中执行：cat /mnt/shared/needs/requirements.md。返回文档的完整内容，以便理解需求并撰写产品规格文档。"}', 'name': 'skill_loader'}, 'id': 'tool-e05296b2eb78429ebbb0a03d24ab10f6', 'index': 1, 'type': 'function'}]}, 'finish_reason': 'tool_calls', 'index': 0, 'logprobs': None}], 'object': 'chat.completion', 'usage': {'prompt_tokens': 4447, 'completion_tokens': 316, 'total_tokens': 4763, 'completion_tokens_details': {'reasoning_tokens': 169}, 'prompt_tokens_details': {'cached_tokens': 4031}}, 'created': 1776344282, 'system_fingerprint': None, 'model': 'glm-5.1', 'id': 'chatcmpl-cbd08f7c-5c2b-97b6-9384-049c6d7c0a4c'}
